# ar-db-handler has no required environment variables.
# This file exists for project-layout parity with sibling modules.
#
# Callers typically pass DB paths directly to init_filings_db() /
# init_metrics_db(). If your application reads a path from the
# environment, document it here, e.g.:
#
# AR_FILINGS_DB_PATH=/path/to/filings.db
# AR_METRICS_DB_PATH=/path/to/metrics.db
